  <h3>Why Foreplay Matters</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><span class="highlight">Builds anticipation:</span> Foreplay creates excitement and eagerness, making the main act more enjoyable.</li>
    <li><span class="highlight">Increases physical readiness:</span> It helps increase blood flow and natural lubrication, reducing discomfort.</li>
    <li><span class="highlight">Enhances emotional connection:</span> Taking time to explore each other’s bodies fosters intimacy and trust.</li>
  </ul>

  <div class="image-container">
    <img src="https://silkharmony.in/images/foreplay.png" alt="Couple enjoying foreplay" />
  </div>

